ted her PhD in English at Harvard in 2017 crafted The Chair a new miniseries.";i:14;s:41:"Watch the trailer for Netflixs The Chair.";i:15;s:199:"The six-part series which drops on Netflix tonight August 20 explores race and privilege the battle between the old world order and the new and the fact that sometimes getting everything you want is.";i:16;s:23:"Sandra Oh in The Chair.";i:17;s:158:"I feel like I arrived at the party after the last call says Ji-Yoon Kim Sandra Ohs embattled character in Netflixs new compelling six-episode drama The Chair.";i:18;s:134:"Shes referring to the timing of becoming chair of an English department at a fictional lesser Ivy when the academy and humanities are.";i:19;s:269:"A whole new comedy drama series breaking new ground by focussing intimately on the lives of academics the Netflix comedy drama series titled The Chair stars the impeccable Sandra Oh as its protagonist and that is just the first of the many things the series gets right.";i:20;s:59:"The first season of The Chair will debut on Netflix on Aug.";i:21;s:125:"A comedy series set in the English department of a stuffy university doesnt sound like itd be a laugh riot but The Chair isn.";i:22;s:72:"So far reviews for Netflixs The Chair have been overwhelmingly positive.";i:23;s:72:"Its release timed as a new school year begins could not be more perfect.";i:24;s:94:"Season 1 of the series came out on August 20 and the internet has been buzzing about it since.";i:25;s:28:"The Chair On Netflix Review.";i:26;s:214:"Sandra Ohs Compelling Campus Drama Is Too Rushed To Make Any Pertinent Points The show tackles the demise of English Literature as a discipline with a light-touch preferring to focus on the drama around it instead.";i:27;s:40:"Posted on August 23 2021 August 23 2021.";i:28;s:25:"The Chair Netflix review.";i:29;s:71:"Finally we have a worthy showcase for Sandra Ohs cracking comic timing.";i:30;s:84:"In Netflixs new dramedy The Chair Sandra Oh plays Dr Ji-Yoon Kim the new